iv><div class="t m0 x3f h1a y129 ff11 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls47 ws0">（二）<span class="_ _a"></span> <span class="_ _15"> </span><span class="ff12 ls0">问<span class="ff5 fs3">：<span class="_ _6"></span>我是宗教研究中心的硕士。<span class="_ _6"></span>您刚才讲到，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y12a ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学术研究和修持所得的结论不一样，<span class="_ _5"></span>那么请问，<span class="_ _5"></span>学术研究能</div><div class="t m0 x9 hb y12b ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">不能与修持很好地结合起来？ </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
